    "\", p.189 11 Zetzsche, Arner [2] Compromised privacy Given the cloud and DLT operate on arrays of servers rather than individual single servers, saving data in the cloud or on a DLT means spreading data over multiple servers.",
    "Data protection and privacy violations are potentially very costly to institutions relying on DeFi.",
    "\", p.189-190 11 Zetzsche, Arner [2] Tech dependency Connectivity DeFi in whatever form increases technological security risks due to tech dependency and connectivity\", p. 190 11 Zetzsche, Arner [2] Infrastructure \"[T]he ongoing concentration in crucial financial market infrastructure and the underlying tech industry furthers a techmonoculture which facilitates cyberattacks.",
